title: Central Catholic's Dana Roberts is lehighvalleylive Girls Volleyball Player of the Week
text:
By Kyle Craig | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 11, 2015 4:15 PM 
GIRLS VOLLEYBALL PLAYER OF THE WEEK Dana Roberts (Crosscourt Volleyball Club photo) 
Dana Roberts , Central Catholic 
The junior outside hitter starred last weekend as the Vikings placed third at State Collegeâ€™s Little Lion Invitational. 
Roberts then recorded 19 kills and 22 digs as Central Catholic topped Emmaus in five sets on Monday. She tacked on 11 kills and 10 digs in a sweep of Whitehall on Wednesday. 
The Vikings, ranked No. 3 by lehighvalleylive, were No. 10 in the latest Class AA Pennsylvania Volleyball Coaches Association poll. 
Honorable mention : Jr. S Julia Bradford , Central Catholic; Sr. OH Taylor Frisoli , Notre Dame; Sr. S Kristin Krause , Parkland; Sr. S Brooke Lichty , Nazareth; Sr. MH Bre McDonald , Nazareth; So. MH Grace Mittl , Liberty; So. OH Julia Roman , Freedom; Sr. OP Siena Salvaggio , Parkland; So. MH Hailey Silfies , Freedom.
